com.gwtplatform.dispatch.rpc.client.gin

Class RpcDispatchAsyncModule

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.google.gwt.inject.client.AbstractGinModule
      • com.gwtplatform.dispatch.client.gin.AbstractDispatchAsyncModule
        • com.gwtplatform.dispatch.rpc.client.gin.RpcDispatchAsyncModule
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    GinModule

    public class RpcDispatchAsyncModule
extends AbstractDispatchAsyncModule
    An implementation of AbstractDispatchAsyncModule that uses Remote Procedure Calls (RPC).

    This gin module provides provides access to the DispatchAsync singleton, which is used to make calls to the server over RPC.

    If you want to prevent XSRF attack (you use secured Actions) the empty DefaultSecurityCookieAccessor could leave your application vulnerable to XSRF attacks.
